csdl.jupiter.event
Class ReviewEvent

java.lang.Object
  csdl.jupiter.event.ReviewEvent

public class ReviewEvent
extends java.lang.Object

Provides review event. This wraps this with an event type and event kind. This is used for the argument of the reviewInvoked in the IReviewListener interface.

Version:
$Id: ReviewEvent.java,v 1.8 2005/03/28 14:39:31 takuyay Exp $
Author:
Takuya Yamashita
